data.title: Another Camp Rock DCOM Extra... Yeahyuhhh (Plus more!)
data.meta_description: It's about time (LOL JB reference) that we had a Nick picture on here ;) He's pictured with Jordan Francis. Credit goes to thekellyaffair at callusfreaks It talks about Demi Lovato, Alyson Stoner, Anna Maria Perez de Tagle, Meghan Jette Martin, and Jasmine Richards. Link:…
